{"type":"message","id":"6e01a63e","parentId":"641a007a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T17:55:27.879Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/2573fcc8-01be-471b-9852-0840e0303062.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/2573fcc8-01be-471b-9852-0840e0303062.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-03-21 01:55:27 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b54ecee2f78a0b36b7decbc0389a, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ecee2f78a0b36b7decbc0389a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 01:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/2573fcc8-01be-471b-9852-0840e0303062.jpg"}],"timestamp":1774029327877}}
