{"type":"message","id":"b6d9e988","parentId":"676f06d6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:43:33.472Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 02:39:03 GMT+8] Exec completed (dawn-orb, code 0) :: - Resolving jx76-gog ✔ OK. Installed jx76-gog -> /home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/jx76-gog\nSystem: [2026-03-21 02:43:32 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b54ed1b8ead30b3fca7f24601857]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ed1b8ead30b3fca7f24601857\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 02:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\nhttps://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QmIRg9iC501s9qJw1iXWVg学习这个"}],"timestamp":1774032213468}}
{"type":"message","id":"ebde301f","parentId":"b6d9e988","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:43:48.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发了一个微信文章的链接，要求我学习这个内容。这是一个微信公众号文章链接。\n\n我需要：\n1. 获取这个链接的内容\n2. 分析/总结内容\n3. 学习其中的知识\n\n让我先尝试抓取这个网页内容。我可以使用miaoda-web-fetch技能或者直接用curl/wget来获取。","thinkingSignature":"7d6b022c7d25faeeee3c14579ab112670a3bee2f364c91790e75067ef2274bf0"},{"type":"text","text":"姚总发了一个微信文章链接，让我获取并学习内容。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_87txr9izq76j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-fetch/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":120,"cacheRead":89185,"cacheWrite":928,"totalTokens":90370,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.000144,"cacheRead":0.0026755499999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00011135999999999999,"total":0.0029720099999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032213470}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a9a55b1","parentId":"ebde301f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:43:48.402Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_87txr9izq76j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-fetch\r\ndescription: \"Use when user needs to crawl or fetch a specific URL to extract/summarize its content. Provides necessary command usage instructions for fetching known URLs. 触发词：网页抓取, 抓取网页, 提取网页内容, web crawl, 爬取, fetch url, 总结网页, 抓取 URL, 读取网页\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_fetch\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Fetch\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` 抓取指定网页内容，由 AI 自动总结/提取。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--url` | 网页 URL | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary（见 miaoda-web-search skill）\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL（见 miaoda-web-search skill）→ web-crawl 提取详情\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 抓取指定 URL 并提取信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url https://example.com/pricing\r\n\r\n# 搜索 → 深入抓取：先搜索找到目标 URL，再抓取提取详细信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url <搜索结果中的URL>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`（见 miaoda-web-search skill） |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774032228380}}
{"type":"message","id":"34ee1a37","parentId":"5a9a55b1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:43:51.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要使用miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl来抓取微信文章内容。让我执行这个命令。","thinkingSignature":"23de40278be6fa78ffe4767528b73df9d7dab054e0fa6596a28338b8fec84fcf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sj2tnypfwylo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QmIRg9iC501s9qJw1iXWVg\" 2>&1","timeout":60000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53405,"output":101,"cacheRead":37443,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90949,"cost":{"input":0.016021499999999998,"output":0.00012119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011232899999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017265989999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032228401}}
