{"type":"message","id":"9b33f7a9","parentId":"23a5677d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:44:58.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总说\"研究解决这个问题，之前都读出来了\"，意思是之前我可以读取微信文章的，现在不行了。\n\n让我研究一下之前为什么能读，现在不能读的问题。可能是：\n1. 网络问题\n2. 需要用特定的方式\n3. 微信有反爬机制\n\n让我先尝试用其他方式抓取这个页面。我可以尝试：\n1. 用其他工具\n2. 检查之前成功的方法\n\n之前我用的是miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl，但它没有返回内容。让我尝试其他方式。","thinkingSignature":"9a57f1df0febd8cd2cefd56dfc0e587281fffe8dff5eae61ef47a4be26dc66c6"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我研究一下。之前可能用其他方式能读取。让我尝试几种方法：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_09un408oa6y6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -A \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36\" \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QmIRg9iC501s9qJw1iXWVg\" 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":247,"cacheRead":89830,"cacheWrite":1886,"totalTokens":92100,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0002964,"cacheRead":0.0026948999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00022632,"total":0.0032587199999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032288118}}
