{"type":"message","id":"923fcff6","parentId":"9b858a2f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:45:07.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"curl能获取到HTML内容，但这是需要JavaScript渲染的内容。让我尝试提取文章的实际文本内容。可能需要解析HTML中的某些部分。让我用grep或sed来提取文章内容。","thinkingSignature":"827ae40e90a145c76b891336de7c800def76ca8f820318d1b400f5a44a0f2367"},{"type":"text","text":"能获取到HTML，让我提取其中的文章文本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q873xbicpr9m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -A \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\" \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QmIRg9iC501s9qJw1iXWVg\" 2>&1 | grep -oP '(?<=id=\"js_content\">)[\\s\\S]*?(?=</div>)' | head -1 | sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | tr -s ' ' | head -200","timeout":30000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55624,"output":200,"cacheRead":37443,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93267,"cost":{"input":0.0166872,"output":0.00023999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0011232899999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01805049}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032298935}}
