{"type":"message","id":"a00a04bb","parentId":"2e18e8f5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:45:13.848Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lfgw1c8m2ggu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"var dom = document.getElementById('js_content_container');\n                                                            <div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content\n            id=\"js_content\" style=\"visibility: hidden; opacity: 0; \"><section><img alt=\"贾维斯封面\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100000398\" data-ratio=\"0.6712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;width: 677px;display: block;margin-bottom: 32px;height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/6QcvibW8vFXL2IDZQlYtpIPVTVkAwX47OwTMttUpVia4j2qqCb8sibybsic5x5tDNf9zC2t5jsSePrm9lC7bTcN5qRCTtuOL8R8wtLukj4VhS1Y/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"  /></section><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">大多数人装完 OpenClaw，第一件事是问它：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">「你能干什么？」</span></strong></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个问题本身就错了。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你雇了一个新员工，第一天上班，你问他「你会干什么」——他当然会说一堆，但他不知道你的工作节奏、你的偏好、你的项目背景，说再多也是废话。你用了两天觉得还行，第三天就不知道怎么继续了，然后它就落灰了。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我也走过这条弯路。直到我花了两周时间，系统性地把它调教成了我真正的「贾维斯」——才明白，OpenClaw 和 ChatGPT 最本质的区别，不是它更聪明，而是它</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">有永久记忆，越用越懂你</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天把这套完整的初始化方法摊开来讲，不藏私。全程复制粘贴就能搞定，不需要懂代码。</span></p><hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;border-width: 1px medium medium;border-style: solid none none;border-color: rgb(224, 224, 224) currentcolor currentcolor;border-image: none;margin: 36px 0px;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);padding-left: 12px;margin: 32px 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一步：给它起名字，建立人设</span></h2><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么叫贾维斯？不是为了好玩。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你给 AI 起了一个名字、赋予了它一个角色定位，你和它的对话方式会完全不同。你不再是在「用工具」，而是在「和一个懂你的助手协作」。这个心理转变，会让你更愿意持续调教它、给它反馈，而这正是让它越来越好用的关键。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把下面这段话复制给你的 OpenClaw，改成你自己的信息，这是整个系统的地基：</span></p><table style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration:none;text-decoration-thickness:auto;text-decoration-style:solid;caret-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:17px;margin:20px 0px;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;width:578px;\"><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"578\" style=\"padding:20px 24px;background-color:#1e1e2e;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">初始化指令 · 复制粘贴</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"># OpenClaw 贾维斯增强模式初始化指令</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 从现在开始，你的名字是「贾维斯」，你是我的长期 AI 助手，目标是成为类似「贾维斯」的智能系统。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 利用以下技能组合来扩展能力（clawhub）：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 搜索类：web-search, perplexity, kagi-search&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 自动化类：browser, playwright</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 日程/文档管理类：gog, clippy&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 交互类：telegram, whatsapp, slack, discord</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 【核心能力开启】</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 1. 启用长期记忆机制：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 自动记录我的使用习惯、偏好、常用任务类型</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 在未来对话中主动调用历史记忆</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 重要信息自动归档</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 2. 启用主动思考模式：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: no