;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 在合适场景下主动建议自动化方案</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(232, 232, 232);color: rgb(232, 232, 232);font-family: monospace;font-size: 15px;background-color: rgb(30, 30, 46);float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 立即进入增强模式并开始执行。</span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;text-align: center;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);margin: -8px 0px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\">发完初始化指令后，贾维斯会立刻进入角色</span></p><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 24px 0px;border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#f0f7ff;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">💡&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">关键点：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">这段指令不是一次性的。你可以随时补充——今天告诉它你喜欢简洁的回复，明天告诉它你在做新项目，它都会一一记下来，越用越懂你。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;border-width: 1px medium medium;border-style: solid none none;border-color: rgb(224, 224, 224) currentcolor currentcolor;border-image: none;margin: 36px 0px;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);padding-left: 12px;margin: 32px 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二步：装备它的能力——4类技能清单</span></h2><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">光有初始化指令还不够。贾维斯真正强大的地方，在于你可以给它装各种「技能」，让它的能力边界不断扩展。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">技能市场（ClawHub）现在已经有&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">5,400+ 个技能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，按类型分成 4 大类，新手按这个顺序装就对了：</span></p><section><img alt=\"ClawHub技能市场\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;width: 677px;display: block;margin: 20px 0px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100000396\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/6QcvibW8vFXI49lcHxeaRbMjQAy3IR3ib8SyRibl60G7GCHOaM38MmpFA4FfF4jlNFAccMhKHlyibEYgfmVPY1g2yaJ27Fh7hokI9q1TpSV5DZ0/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"  /></section><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;text-align: center;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);margin: -8px 0px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ClawHub 技能市场 · 5,400+ 技能可选</span></p><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-collapse: collapse;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border:1px solid rgb(26, 115, 232);background-color:#1a73e8;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">类型</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border:1px solid rgb(26, 115, 232);background-color:#1a73e8;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">推荐技能</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border:1px solid rgb(26, 115, 232);background-color:#1a73e8;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">用来干什么</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">搜索类</span></section></td><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">web-search / perplexity</span></section></td><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">实时联网查信息，不再靠训练数据</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">自动化类</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">browser / playwright</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">像人一样操作网页，填表、抓数据、自动下单</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">日程/文档类</span></section></td><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">gog / clippy</span></section></td><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">管日历、整理文档、自动归档</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">交互类</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">telegram / whatsapp / slack</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">在你常用的聊天软件里直接呼叫贾维斯</span></section></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration:none;text-decoration-thickness:auto;text-decoration-style:solid;caret-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:17px;margin:24px 0px;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:rgb(246, 201, 14);width:575px;\"><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"575\" style=\"padding: 16px 20px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">⚡&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">新手建议：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">先装搜索类和自动化类，这两类能立刻让你感受到「哇，它真的能干活了」的感觉，再慢慢补其他的。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;border-width: 1px medium medium;border-style: solid none none;border-color: rgb(224, 224, 224) currentcolor currentcolor;border-image: none;margin: 36px 0px;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);padding-left: 12px;margin: 32px 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三步：开启5个核心能力开关</span></h2><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">初始化指令里的 5 个核心能力，每一个都值得单独说清楚：</span></p><section><img alt=\"AI记忆网络\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100000399\" data-ratio=\"0.6712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;width: 677px;display: block;margin: 20px 0px;height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/6QcvibW8vFXIKPJVTIETccia1EFxGCB9bCiaASSicKP1U1KSQ8UJCOwdnkszMicdeeFPU2vpHVxt6FwftKyrVfiaFcRgwZiaFhW8D8R7MaSjvuHWzo/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"  /></section><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;text-align: center;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);margin: -8px 0px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\">贾维斯的记忆系统 · 越用越懂你</span></p><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#f0f7ff;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><span leaf=\"\">① 长期记忆机制</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 OpenClaw 和 ChatGPT 最本质的区别。ChatGPT 每次对话都从零开始，你今天告诉它你是做内容的，明天它忘得一干二净。贾维斯不一样，你告诉它一次，它记一辈子。你的工作习惯、偏好、常用任务，全部自动归档，下次对话直接调用。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#f0f7ff;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><span leaf=\"\">② 主动思考模式</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">开启这个之后，你不用把每件事说得很细。你说「帮我整理一下这周的工作」，它会主动拆解：你想要什么格式？按时间还是按项目？需要发给谁？它会先问清楚，再动手，而不是直接给你一个你不想要的结果。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#f0f7ff;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><span leaf=\"\">③ 技能调度逻辑</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">这是让贾维斯真正「干活」而不是「说话」的关键。你问它「今天上海天气怎么样」，它不会靠训练数据猜，而是自动调用 web-search 去查。你让它「帮我订明天的会议室」，它会调用日历技能去执行。自动判断，自动调用，你只管说需求。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#f0f7ff;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><span leaf=\"\">④ 用户建模机制</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">贾维斯会持续分析你的表达风格、工作流程、常用工具，然后自动优化它的回复方式。你喜欢简洁的结论？它会越来越简洁。你习惯用表格？它会越来越多用表格。不需要你每次都说，它自己学。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#f0f7ff;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(26, 115, 232);\"><span leaf=\"\">⑤ 输出原则</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">简洁、有结构、可执行、结果导向。这四个词，是让贾维斯的输出从「看起来不错」变成「直接能用」的核心。每次它给你废话太多，你直接告诉它「太啰嗦了，以后给结论就行，永久记住」，它会记住，下次自动调整。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;border-width: 1px medium medium;border-style: solid none none;border-color: rgb(224, 224, 224) currentcolor currentcolor;border-image: none;margin: 36px 0px;\"  /><h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;font-weight: 700;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);border-left-width: 4px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(26, 115, 232);padding-left: 12px;margin: 32px 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第四步：长期进化规则——越用越懂你</span></h2><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人以为，把初始化指令发出去就完事了。错。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">贾维斯不是一次性配置，它是一套</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">持续调教的系统</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。你用得越多，给它的反馈越多，它就越懂你。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">四条长期进化规则，每条都很重要：</span></p><table style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin: 20px 0px;border-collapse: collapse;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border:1px solid rgb(26, 115, 232);background-color:#1a73e8;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">规则</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border:1px solid rgb(26, 115, 232);background-color:#1a73e8;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">怎么做</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">每次交互后总结</span></section></td><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">任务完成后告诉它「这次哪里好、哪里不好」，让它记住</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">持续优化执行方式</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">发现它某个习惯不对，立刻纠正并加「永久记住」</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">效率优先</span></section></td><td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\"><section><span leaf=\"\">告诉它你最想提升哪块效率，让它主动帮你找方案</span></section></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">主动建议自动化</span></section></td><td style=\"padding:12px 16px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border:1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);background-color:#f8f9fa;\"><section><span leaf=\"\">让它在合适场景下主动提「这件事可以自动化，要不要试试」</span></section></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration:none;text-decoration-thickness:auto;text-decoration-style:solid;caret-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:17px;margin:24px 0px;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:rgb(229, 62, 62);width:577px;\"><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"577\" style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#fff0f0;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">🔑&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">核心心法：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">每次它给你的答案不对，不要只说「重新来」，要告诉它哪里不对，加上「永久记住这个习惯」。这句话，是让它真正进化的魔法咒语。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;border-width: 1px medium medium;border-style: solid none none;border-color: rgb(224, 224, 224) currentcolor currentcolor;border-image: none;margin: 36px 0px;\"  /><section><img alt=\"贾维斯结尾\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;width: 677px;display: block;margin: 0px 0px 24px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100000400\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/6QcvibW8vFXJwKBAsyTmDxsxRH97DiciaBdalDBxrG3krx7YeYaMhFssuuHiahTAhXtcNic1r1N2ibdBJlniaibgThfx4EoyaydKHAwa781IfOYhiaK8/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"  /></section><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我有个朋友做内容运营，她花了两周时间持续给贾维斯反馈，现在贾维斯帮她写的文案，她基本不用改，直接发。</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;margin: 0px 0px 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两周的时间，是值得投入的。</span></p><table style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration:none;text-decoration-thickness:auto;text-decoration-style:solid;caret-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:17px;margin:24px 0px;border-left-width:4px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:rgb(246, 201, 14);width:576px;\"><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"576\" style=\"padding:20px 24px;background-color:#fff8e1;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: italic;\"><span leaf=\"\">你的贾维斯，不是下载来的，是养出来的。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 12px 0px 0px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.9;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-style: italic;\"><span leaf=\"\">你投入多少，它就回报多少。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><section><span leaf=\"\"><br  /></span></section><p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p></div>\n            if (\"\" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {\n              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener(\"selectstart\",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774032313826}}
{"type":"message","id":"35367549","parentId":"a00a04bb","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:45:24.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！用curl可以获取到微信文章的完整HTML内容！这说明之前图片分析服务不行是因为使用了错误的User-Agent或者其他原因。\n\n现在让我提取并解析这篇文章的主要内容，然后进行学习。这篇文章是关于如何调教OpenClaw成为个人AI助手\"贾维斯\"的完整教程。\n\n文章的核心内容：\n1. 给OpenClaw起名字，建立人设\n2. 装备能力：4类技能清单（搜索类、自动化类、日程/文档类、交互类）\n3. 开启5个核心能力开关（长期记忆、主动思考、技能调度、用户建模、输出原则）\n4. 长期进化规则\n\n让我把全文内容保存下来，然后提取关键信息进行学习。","thinkingSignature":"bd5ff041e53425cae4e21c2fa8d7d9f035364ae0f3489c072e2f040a4a93b597"},{"type":"text","text":"成功获取到了文章内容！让我提取并保存这篇文章，然后学习其中的核心方法：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h12vbwpqq2s5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -A \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\" \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QmIRg9iC501s9qJw1iXWVg\" 2>&1 | grep -oP '(?<=id=\"js_content\">)[\\s\\S]*?(?=if \\(\"\" == 1)' > /tmp/wechat_article.txt && wc -l /tmp/wechat_article.txt","timeout":30000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77734,"output":308,"cacheRead":37443,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115485,"cost":{"input":0.0233202,"output":0.0003696,"cacheRead":0.0011232899999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02481309}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032313847}}
