{"type":"message","id":"0e14f3ea","parentId":"a223087d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:50:18.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总让我停止学习微信文章，改为学习\"弱电商，集成商和代理商\"的知识，想想自己能发挥什么作用。\n\n这是一个新的学习方向：\n1. 弱电行业/电商\n2. 集成商\n3. 代理商\n\n姚总的公司是道简网络，做的是企业数字化解决方案、网络系统集成、智能安防与弱电工程、IT全周期运维服务。这属于弱电行业。\n\n让我开始搜索和学习这些知识，然后每5分钟总结一次。\n\n我需要搜索：\n1. 弱电行业知识\n2. 系统集成商\n3. 代理商模式\n\n然后结合道简网络的业务，思考我能发挥什么作用。\n\n让我开始搜索和学习。","thinkingSignature":"52de261f9c23e8bedf31624aab9c536973c0f5489ad1eca91fa1c67efdeca567"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！姚总让我学习**弱电商、集成商和代理商**的知识，结合道简网络的业务，思考我能发挥什么作用。\n\n立刻开始，每5分钟汇报一次，不停下！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tani3secpai6_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":220,"cacheRead":118353,"cacheWrite":412,"totalTokens":119122,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.00026399999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0035505899999999997,"cacheWrite":0.000049439999999999994,"total":0.0039051299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032608315}}
{"type":"message","id":"a466e6ce","parentId":"0e14f3ea","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:50:18.184Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tani3secpai6_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774032618164}}
{"type":"message","id":"019469d6","parentId":"a466e6ce","timestamp":"2026-03-20T18:50:21.887Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在开始搜索学习弱电行业、集成商、代理商的相关知识。","thinkingSignature":"2508a5beb5b77fa41b57e619d323275b9d0407b9d76a8175733120058f62fcc9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7wjb6mk5yt0g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"弱电行业 系统集成商 工程商 代理商 商业模式\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":60000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82194,"output":83,"cacheRead":37443,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119720,"cost":{"input":0.024658199999999998,"output":0.0000996,"cacheRead":0.0011232899999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025881089999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774032618183}}
